PROJECT.NAME: icAstAngu6-mito
PROJECT.TITLE: Astagobius angustatus, draft mitochondrial assembly, icAstAngu6-mito.
PROJECT.DESCRIPTION: This project provides a draft mitochondrial assembly of Astagobius angustatus. The assembly is provided by the European Reference Genome Atlas (ERGA, https://www.erga-biodiversity.eu/) via the Biodiversity Genomics Europe project (BGE, https://biodiversitygenomics.eu/).
